---
import BaseLayout from "../../components/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="文章 / Writing - MrFung" description="MrFung 的文章目录，记录全栈、AICoding、独立产品和运动实践。">
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="section">
      <p class="page-kicker">Writing</p>
      <h1>文章 / Writing</h1>
      <div class="bilingual intro-copy">
        <p>这里会放全栈开发、AICoding、独立产品和运动实践相关的文章。当前先用自我介绍作为稳定入口。</p>
        <p>This space will collect notes on full-stack development, AICoding, independent products, and endurance practice. A short self-introduction is here as the first stable entry.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="writing-list">
        <article class="article-card">
          <div>
            <span class="lang-label">Profile</span>
            <h2>自我介绍：把工程、AICoding 和耐力运动放在一起</h2>
            <div class="bilingual">
              <p>一篇用于占位的自我介绍，说明我关注什么、在做什么，以及为什么把产品和运动放在同一个长期节奏里。</p>
              <p>A placeholder self-introduction about what I build, what I care about, and why product craft and endurance practice share the same rhythm.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/writing/self-introduction/">阅读 / Read</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
